1 26.1 - 08.1 - 05. Statute of limitations .
2 A cause of action against the association or the board must be commenced within the
3 earlier of one year after the cause of action occurs or December 31, 2027 .
4 SECTION 2. REPEAL. Chapters 26.1-08 and 26.1-08.1 of the North Dakota Century Code
5 are repealed.
6 SECTION 3. EFFECTIVE DATE. Section 2 of this Act becomes effective December 31,
7 2027.
8 SECTION 4. EMERGENCY. This Act is declared to be an emergency measure.
